conditionally_allowed: Canned Coconut Milk (with no guar gum)
Ice Cream (made with clean label ingredients)
Hijiki (cooked only, due to arsenic risk)
Propionates (calcium or sodium, in small amounts)
harmful_ingredients: Lactic Acid Esters of Mono- and Diglycerides
Imitation Ice Cream (with mono- and diglycerides)
Ice Cream Toppings (artificial color and corn syrup)
Cola Drinks (caramel color and phosphoric acid)
Diacetyl Tartaric Acid Esters of Mono- and Diglycerides (DATEM)
Artificial Blue Food Coloring (Patent Blue V)
Snack Mix with Synthetic Flavor Dust
Chocolate Syrup (with high fructose corn syrup)
